1. *Uloge* u ovoj predstavi su odlično izvedene. (Roles in this play were performed excellently.)
2. Naše *uloge* u ovom projektu su definisane i jasne. (Our roles in this project are defined and clear.)
3. *Uloge* za ovu pozorišnu predstavu su već raspoređene. (Roles for this theatre play are already assigned.)
4. Ovaj glumac igra glavnu *ulogu* u predstavi. (This actor plays the main role in the play.)
5. Kada igram društvenu igru, volim da mijenjam *uloge* sa drugima. (When I play a board game, I like to switch roles with others.)
6. Ne mogu da obavim svoje *uloge* u firmi bez pristupa računaru. (I can't perform my roles in the company without access to the computer.)
7. Svaka osoba ima svoje *uloge* u društvu. (Every person has their roles in society.)
8. *Uloge* u ovom filmu su veoma zahtevne i izazovne. (Roles in this movie are very demanding and challenging.)
9. Ona je vrlo uspješno odigrala svoju *ulogu* u školskoj predstavi. (She played her role in the school play very successfully.)
10. Na sastanku smo razgovarali o našim *ulogama* u budućim projektima. (At the meeting, we discussed our roles in future projects.)